Step1: 	run equillibrium sims
		namd3 +p2 +devices 0 system_eq.namd > eq000.log
		Now you will have coor, vel and xsc files

Step2: make folders bstates, common_files and westpa_scripts

Step3: cd bstates
		mkdir eq0
		cd eq0
		cp ../../myfiles/system_eq000.coor seg.coor
		cp ../../myfiles/system_eq000.dcd seg.dcd
		cp ../../myfiles/system_eq000.vel seg.vel
		cp ../../myfiles/system_eq000.xsc seg.xsc
		cd ..
		touch bstates.txt
		echo "0 1.0 eq0" > bstates.txt

Step4: cd ../common_files/
		cp ../../myfiles/*.psf .
		cp ../../myfiles/*.pdb .
		Note: Also keep a md.conf

Step5: cd ../westpa_scripts/
		cp calc_pcoord.py .
		cp get_pcoord.sh .
		cp runseg.sh .

Step6: copy west.cfg, env.sh, init.sh and tstate.file in the root directory
		Note: root directory is the main directory, like lets say you are making a directory for NorA, then inside it will be these four files and then those three folders


Step7: ./init.sh ===>>> this will make the west.h5

Step8: w_run --n-workers 4 & > west.log &

How to kill: ps aux | grep w_run
				pkill -f 12345 or kill 12345

